dct_title_s: La description de la Terre Saincte
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Illustrations of ships and settlements throughout.
Shows topography, drainage, vegetation, places of historical interest.
Index below map: Les lieux specifiez en ceste carte, & situation d'iceux, par observation des degrez de leur longitude & latitude.
